		br
	.container
		.row
			.col.s12.m4
				.center.promo
					i.material-icons.large.light-blue-text.text-darken-3 visibility_off
					p.promo-caption Reserve Your Place
					p.light.center
						| Get a .o domain for FREE today and claim your place on the OpenNIC network, a user owned and controlled Network Information Center offering a democratic alternative to the traditional ICANN Top-Level Domain registries.
			.col.s12.m4
				.center.promo
					i.material-icons.large.light-green-text lock
					p.promo-caption Free SSL Certificate
					p.light.center
						| Every domain registration comes with a corresponding SSL certificate signed by the
						a(href='https://www.moderntld.com/ca') ModernTLD CA
						| . Note: These certificates are untrusted by default in most major browsers because OpenNIC is not a part of the ICANN network. You will have to
						a(href='https://www.moderntld.com/ca') install it manually
						| . This is normal behavior.
			.col.s12.m4
				.center.promo
					i.material-icons.large.red-text dns
					p.promo-caption Resiliant DNS
					p.light.center
						| We not only operate two authoratative "Tier 1" servers for the root zone, but our zone is replicated across a multitude of Tier 1 and Tier 2 servers, ensuring your site can virtually never go down due to DNS issues. Check out the list of
						a(href='https://servers.opennicproject.org/') OpenNIC servers
						|  or
						a(href='http://health.moderntld.com/') ModernTLD Health Statistics
						| .
